==Personal life==
In his fourth year of middle school, Morozov met Veronika Gorbachev, an eventual police officer. After dating for eight years, Gorbachev proposed in 1986, to which Morozov accepted, and they married that same year. Their son, [[Ilya Morozov (V1.2.1)|Ilya]], was born in 1994.

